title: Jules Verne - 20,000 Leagues Under the Sea (read by David Case)
description:
I downloaded this audiobook from Audible and used audible-activator and ffmpeg to remove encryption from it.

This book is read by David Case under the pseudonym Frederick Davidson. He has also narrated these audiobooks:

On the Origin of Species by Charles Darwin (magnet:?xt=urn:btih:d09984387f9df6832bd4073aa637ec70f7d1e9cc)
